{"categories":["others","computer-internet","business-services","transactional","marketing-and-design"],"collections":"survey-campaign","description":"Engage your audience with a dynamic and interactive email template that perfectly blends sleek design and functionality. This digital masterpiece embodies a light, sans serif typography, enhanced by vibrant blue and orange illustrations. The template incorporates modern technology elements such as emojis and a megaphone, which add a fun and playful touch, making it a perfect choice for business services, software, and technology sectors. With its focus on surveys and questionnaires, it allows you to gather valuable opinions and feedback. Its clean white background ensures your content stands out, making it an excellent tool for transactional communication and marketing design. This template is not just about asking questions, it's about sparking conversations and creating meaningful connections.","short_description":"Engage your audience with this dynamic email template, blending sleek design and functionality. Perfect for business services, software, and technology sectors, it features vibrant illustrations, playful emojis, and a megaphone. Gather valuable feedback with its focus on surveys and questionnaires. Ideal for transactional communication and marketing design.","designer":{"avatar_url":"https://d1oco4z2z1fhwp.cloudfront.net/designers/matteo-della-chiesa.jpg","description":"I've started to use Photoshop when I was 13. From 2009 to 2014, I've been a part of 5 Art Groups, doing Illustrations and Photo-manipulations, collaborating with over 150 Artists from all the Planet. In 2014, during my final school's exams, I've got my first Freelance Job at a Milan based Agency. Thanks to that first project, I started my Career as a Freelance Independent UI & Web Designer. Today, I help brands improve their online and digital presence, building usable, unique & beautiful products, mostly collaborating with Italian & US Ag